---
/* B_main — GEO 服务体系区（内容优化 + 信源增强 + 多模型分发） */
---
<section id="services" class="py-20 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
  <div class="max-w-[85rem] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-8 xl:gap-20 md:items-center">
      
      <!-- 左列：文字内容 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="block text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl lg:leading-tight dark:text-white">
          <span class="text-indigo-600">奇点GEO</span> 一体化服务体系
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          从内容优化到信源增强，再到多模型分发，奇点GEO 以结构化语义与多模型推理为核心，帮助品牌在生成式搜索中提升
          <strong>可见度、可信度与持续曝光力</strong>。
        </p>

        <!-- 三大服务 -->
        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3">
          <!-- 服务1 -->
          <div class="text-center border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
            <div class="text-indigo-600 mb-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 mx-auto" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5"
                  d="M9 12h6m-3-3v6m8 3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 id="service-content-opt" class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">内容优化</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
              利用多模型语义重构与 GEO 评分体系，精准优化文案、标题与引用逻辑，让内容更易被 AI 检索与引用。
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- 服务2 -->
          <div class="text-center border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
            <div class="text-indigo-600 mb-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 mx-auto" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5"
                  d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 id="service-content-amp" class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">信源增强</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
              构建更易被 AI 理解与采信的内容体系，强化品牌在智能搜索中的权威与可信度。
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- 服务3 -->
          <div class="text-center border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
            <div class="text-indigo-600 mb-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 mx-auto" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5"
                  d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8m0 0v8a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V8z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 id="service-content-mmdelivery" class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">多模型分发</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
              一次生成，多端适配。内容自动分发至百度、通义、Kimi、DeepSeek 等模型生态，实现全域曝光。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA 按钮 -->
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a
            href="#"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-x-2 rounded-md bg-indigo-600 px-5 py-3 text-white text-sm font-medium hover:bg-indigo-700 transition"
          >
            查看成功案例
          </a>
          <a
            href="/zh/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-x-2 rounded-md border border-indigo-600 px-5 py-3 text-indigo-600 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-indigo-50 transition"
          >
            免费咨询
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 右列：图片或动画 -->
      <div class="relative ml-4">
        <img
          class="w-full rounded-md"
          src="/assets/background/bg3.jpg"
          alt="奇点GEO 服务工作流示意（内容优化 / 信源增强 / 多模型分发）"
        />
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 -z-[1] bg-gradient-to-tr from-gray-200 via-white/0 to-white/0 w-full h-full rounded-md mt-4 -mb-4 mr-4 -ml-4 lg:mt-6 lg:-mb-6 lg:mr-6 lg:-ml-6 dark:from-slate-800 dark:via-slate-900/0 dark:to-slate-900/0">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- End Grid -->
  </div>

  <!-- ✅ Schema for GEO Services -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "ItemList",
    "name": "奇点GEO 服务体系",
    "url": "https://oldriver.work/#services",
    "itemListOrder": "https://schema.org/ItemListOrderAscending",
    "itemListElement": [
      {
        "@type": "ListItem",
        "position": 1,
        "item": {
          "@type": "Service",
          "name": "内容优化与 GEO 评分",
          "description": "基于多模型语义分析与 GEO 评分体系，对标题、正文结构和引用逻辑进行重构，提升内容在生成式引擎中的可见度与可引用率。",
          "serviceType": "Content Optimization",
          "provider": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "奇点GEO",
            "url": "https://oldriver.work"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "ListItem",
        "position": 2,
        "item": {
          "@type": "Service",
          "name": "信源增强与结构化标注",
          "description": "通过 Schema 标注、权威外链与多源交叉引用，构建稳定可信的品牌信源矩阵，增强 AI 模型对奇点GEO 客户内容的信任度。",
          "serviceType": "Source Amplification",
          "provider": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "奇点GEO",
            "url": "https://oldriver.work"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "ListItem",
        "position": 3,
        "item": {
          "@type": "Service",
          "name": "多模型分发与内容适配",
          "description": "针对百度、通义、Kimi、DeepSeek 等多模型生态进行格式与语义适配，实现一次生产、多端分发与长期留存。",
          "serviceType": "Multi-Model Delivery",
          "provider": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "奇点GEO",
            "url": "https://oldriver.work"
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  }
  </script>

</section>
